author: Corridor Crew
description:
Wren explains to Sam and Jordan how this epic scene from the original Mission Impossible movie was filmed.
The style and characteristics of this sequence alone defined the future of the MI franchise, aiming to create the most exciting action scenes possible for every movie.
title: How they made Tom Cruise's Face Flap
